Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:56.49,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,388)}I wasn't trying to spy on you! I just saw Himuro-san head up this way and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:55.65,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,324)}Kogure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:57.78,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.53,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,383)}K-Kogure-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,385)}You, go back down to the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:05.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Please, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:08.54,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,381)}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.72,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in here of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:23.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Now, this is where i work. Why should i have to ask for permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:27.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Kasama-san! Why are you working on this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.31,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Relax, it's just a little research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Research?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:36.74,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,389)}This system costs a bundle. The higher-ups wanted us to spend a little more time on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:40.32,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,The first group is already over.I'm busy making a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You've become full of yourself, Kogure-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:42.91,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.16,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! If you're gonna fight, take it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.16,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Himuro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:51.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Himuro-san, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Lemon Angel was a program?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break, it's top secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,But you've got to be kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Why would i have a reason to lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.28,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:22.66,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,388)}I understand how you feel. After all, the person who made the Lemon Angel was a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Kohno Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.53,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yui-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:34.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,389)}Yes. Lemon Angel was actually called L.A.P. test program in artificial human intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Test?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:42.26,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,386)}She wanted to hide the fact it was a program and see how many people would accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:53.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,385)}Wow. Yui-senpai was amazing! But Lemon Angel not being real is a bit of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,See? This is why we can't make an announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.74,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's late. I'll give you a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:08.41,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Umm... about our earlier conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.16,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What about Toro? Wasn't Toro, Suwa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:19.21,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh, that. Miki initially helped Yui in developing L.A.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.46,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,If Yui was the genius, she was the producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:29.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And the first model she chose for Lemon Angel was Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:35.35,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Miki was originally against it, but Yui wore Miki down with her smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:38.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yui was stubborn that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah, that i understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.78,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And lastly, Ann, the main vocalist, was modeled after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.78,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:55.92,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,388)}Yep. Yui was always saying how much she liked you, which is why she used you as her model.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:58.67,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.55,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Yui-senpai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.13,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like i'm gonna cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:13.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no idea that you felt so strongly for me. If you were here right now, i'd give you a big hug!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:21.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But because senpai is no longer among us, it tears at my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if i ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:25.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:29.49,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Why was it that Lemon Angel was disbanded all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,The program was destroyed by a hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Did that have anything to do with Yui-senpai passing away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Nah, that was unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.37,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:44.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the Lemon Angel Program ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:50.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,385)}Yui said, "{\i1}I don't want my songs sung by a machine, but by a person.{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Which is why you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.69,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes, i'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.91,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,About the next audition, would you consider giving it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:15.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I don't know what sort of skill you have, and i can't guarantee you'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:20.67,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,But i'd like to see what it was that Yui saw in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.55,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.84,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah, but remember, i'm not sure how it'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:32.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. That's fine. I just want to hear your singing voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.69,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear senpai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.32,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm finally here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally got to meet Kogure-san, also.{\i0}
