Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:55.64,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Wow, i can feel the tension here. Boy, do i feel out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:08:02.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! You shouldn't complain like that. Just relax, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm Erika Campbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm Minaguchi Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Tomo, huh? Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.36,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You too, Erika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:17.12,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,No, no, just Erika is fine. Don't need to add "san."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.12,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah, 'kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:19.91,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.21,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,S-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.46,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I wonder if i made her mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:33.63,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,387)}Well, there are all sorts of people here, so it's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.26,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Uh, 'kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,She was probably just pissed off. Not everyone is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey! Would you cut out the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:46.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I said that the gloss was almost gone! So why didn't you buy more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,S-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.53,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,She really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yep. There sure are a lot of different people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.72,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,390)}Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:14.72,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,383)}Everyone, quiet please. Before the audition, i felt i should introduce all of you to the staff members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.01,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm Kogure Ryouta, the producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:25.02,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,388)}I look forward to all of you giving the first Lemon Angel a run for their money.Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:31.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,384)}The coaches are Yamashiro Lisa-san, Danny Yamaguchi-san, and Jounouchi Takashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:37.82,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349,387)}And also our video producer, Kaga, and the head of our sales department, Kagoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.82,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,321)}Eh? Himuro isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:42.41,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,385)}Yeah. Wasn't the first group produced by Himuro? Isn't it gonna be him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,If Himuro isn't a part of it, then it feels like something's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.42,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.37,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And then we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:48.83,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.96,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What happened to Himuro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:10:00.22,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,385)}Ah, about that. Himuro Shinya won't be participating in the project this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You're serious? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:09.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And lastly, the leader from the first Lemon Angel, Suwa Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:15.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'll be asking her to take on the role of leader again this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:21.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,389)}She's not part of the staff, but i thought to have her sit in to see how everyone does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:27.75,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,387)}The audition will begin in thirty minutes, so until then, everyone please get yourselves ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:28.33,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Umm, Suwa-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.01,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.43,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:43.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Uh, Kogure-san said he wanted me to come..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Umm, senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,O-One moment, senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:57.28,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Didn't i tell you this already? I said never speak to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:06.79,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me. I'm Yuki Saya. I've always been a Lemon Angel fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:12.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,385)}I was so excited thinking about today, that i couldn't sleep a wink. I'll do my best today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:17.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've been working under the name Hoshi Yayoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:23.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,But i quit in order to focus on singing for the Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.29,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.31,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes, i will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.78,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're different as night and day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Dear Yui-senpai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:50.75,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(352,386)}Why am i being treated like this? Does Suwa-senpai really think i'm that hopeless?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You're acting pretty quiet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Uh, Kogure-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:14.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Umm, is it okay if i just go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:19.44,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Is what Miki said bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:34.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,389)}That's part of it, but this just feels like a different world. I don't think i'll fit in as a Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:42.51,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,387)}Can't be helped. At least give the mic a try, and if you really think you can't, then it's okay to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:49.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yeah. May as well stick around to watch after coming all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:53.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah. I can, can't i?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:58.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Finally cheered up. That's more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:03.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh? But even i feel down sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.07,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353,352)\i1}Who is that girl? A friend of the producer?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.78,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,347)\i1}Which means she's guaranteed to pass?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.78,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,378)}But just eat something sweet and you'll cheer right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yeah, i guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.62,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,351)\i1}That's fraud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and do your job as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:19.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349,384)}I want to sing. I didn't sign on to only look pretty for pictures like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.05,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I've had about enough of that sort of stuff out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:26.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,386)}Yayoi-chan... Boss, i'll talk with her about this and get the whole story...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:30.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349,388)}Shut up! It's too late! Plans have already been made for the magazine. You alone can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:31.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Like i care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You trying to embarrass me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:37.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,386)}Embarrass? Like hell. Just change the schedule, you conservative old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,W-Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:45.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,386)}Well, if you can't stand me so much, then why don't you fire me?! I'm sick of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Fine! Get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.53,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay, i'm gone. Sorry to have troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ignore her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.04,Note_2,,0,0,0,,{\frx12\fry350\pos(323,30)\frz1.701}Ophelia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yayoi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.67,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yayoi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:07.22,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer Hoshi Yayoi, i'm Yuki Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:15.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,387)}Don't worry, i'll be fine. This isn't gonna make me give up. I'm taking this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:19.35,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm taking this chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:44.21,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hoshi Yayoi... i mean Yuki-san is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:47.01,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,So why hasn't she become a singer already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:54.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,388)\i1}It's not just Yuki-san, but everyone's really good. Maybe i should quit now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:59.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Isn't your turn next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.29,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, yeah. Actually, i think i'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:20.21,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,387)}Well aren't you a piece of work. No matter how bad you are, you're guaranteed to be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:20.87,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:25.67,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,387)}Just because you have connections with the producer, don't get overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.05,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,This world isn't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.63,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Eh? Now hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:35.14,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,388)}You're next, aren't you? Hurry up and sing so we can hear how bad you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:40.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,389)}Hah, if this producer thinks you have a chance to succeed, then i doubt he has what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.69,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,He must be crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You over there, silence please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Next. Number 50, Minaguchi Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.87,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yui-senpai, i've had enough! I can't stand this any longer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.83,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Now show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:13.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now watch me surprise all of you with how well i can sing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Tomo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.24,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Horrible. Why is she even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:36.03,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is no good, no good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.83,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really did quit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:52.22,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Sorry! One more time from the beginning please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.72,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay, but only once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.35,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:21.70,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,382)}It's no use. I can't sing like Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:25.83,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Really? But i happen to like your singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:28.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,C-Cut it out please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.63,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped, if you compare yourself to Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:40.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,388)}I think what's important is the way you convey your feelings through your singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:41.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:48.19,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,379)}Yeah. When i listen to your singing, i get a feeling of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.27,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,382)}So, please? Sing for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's important is to convey feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.37,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(362,378)}Senpai, please listen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.46,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.30,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the singing Yui admired so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.35,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.36,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yui-senpai, did you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I threw caution to the wind, but i still feel embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:45.66,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Don't be. It moved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:49.71,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\pos(363,351)}That's it for the first round of auditions. You will be sent the results in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.79,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,If that's your best, i wouldn't get too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear your impression of how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:17.32,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,390)}If we're talking about ability, there are plenty of others that can match her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:21.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I don't see what Yui saw in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:25.74,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Though i didn't ask you about her specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.34,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,That's one step forward, i think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.72,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Going to your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:53.90,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, did you get a responce from the audition last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hmm, nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:20:01.36,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, i'll treat you to some cake later, so don't get too down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.58,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! You're talking as if i'm guaranteed to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.33,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:30.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.61,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are the snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:38.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hm? Huh? She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:25.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.66,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,All right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:35.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Second Lemon Angel group, 20 have passed the first round of selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:43.63,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What was that? Yayoi's trying out for the Lemon Angels? That brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:47.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah. Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:56.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case, then i'll have to do something about it.
