Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:15.66,Betétdal_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,36)}Nazeka kokoro wa nemure nakunatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:24.38,Betétdal_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,36)}Dewa suru yuuki mo nakawari
